title: Chris Cornell - Scream (AAC)
description:
Chris Cornell - Scream (2009)

Ripped using EAC secure mode. AAC encoding with Apple Compressor at 256 kbits/s.

Full album as one M4A file. Chapters added for each song, selectable with iTunes or QuickTime Player. iTunes will make a track for each chapter when burning to CD. I'm not sure if anyone will want an album encoded like this, but I thought it was a good way to do it since the tracks are joined together on the original disc.

2. Time
3. Sweet Revenge
4. Get Up
5. Ground Zero
